 “黑人”明星詹妮弗·刘易斯在跌入“10英尺深的峡谷”后险些丧命https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-ish-star-jenifer-lewis-nearly-died-after-falling-10-feet-into-ravine-3600758?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=black-伊什明星詹妮弗·刘易斯在跌入 10 英尺深的峡谷后险些丧命Elizabeth AubreyWed, 13 Mar 2024 20:42:16 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3600758 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·刘易斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员在新的采访中首次公开了这一事件</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-ish-star-jenifer-lewis-nearly-died-after-falling-10-feet-into-ravine-3600758">《Black-ish》明星詹妮弗·刘易斯 (Jenifer Lewis) 跌入“10 英尺深的峡谷”后险些丧命</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·刘易斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Jenifer-Lewis-Photo-by-Rodin-Eckenroth_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><i>黑人</i>明星詹妮弗·刘易斯 (Jenifer Lewis) 讲述了她两年前度假时从 10 英尺高的阳台上摔下来后濒临死亡的经历。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/tv-blogs/bring-back-black-sitcoms-the-tv-shows-that-taught-me-to-be-me-2650892">带回黑人情景喜剧：这些电视节目教会我做我自己</a></strong></li></ul><p>67 岁的刘易斯首次向美国广播公司<a href="https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Culture/exclusive-jenifer-lewis-opens-harrowing-accident-hardest-year/story?id=107942368" target="_blank" rel="noopener">(ABC) 的</a><i>早安美国</i>主持人罗宾·罗伯茨 (Robin Roberts) 讲述了这次事故和她的康复情况。</p><p>刘易斯解释说，她去非洲旅行是为了庆祝这部情景喜剧的完结，该剧从 2014 年持续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-ish-renewed-for-eighth-and-final-season-2942580">到 2022 年</a>，历经八季。</p><p>刘易斯说：“我本来打算退休并搬回家。我征服了梦想。我环游过世界各地，生活很美好。”</p><p>刘易斯于 2022 年 11 月访问了开普敦和卢旺达，随后前往塞伦盖蒂。</p><p> “当太阳落山时，塞伦盖蒂就没有路灯了。一片漆黑，”她解释道。 “我被护送到小屋、我的房间，但没有人带我参观。我应该被安排参观。我铺好狩猎服，看到甲板上有无边泳池，于是我就出去了。</p><p> “我刚刚意识到我又回到了塞伦盖蒂，我正在走路，突然——<i>砰</i>——我掉进了一个 10 英尺高的干燥峡谷，里面布满了巨石、石头和锋利的岩石。 ” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="詹妮弗·刘易斯讲述了令人痛心的事故" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y6iZzioF1og?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>刘易斯说，阳台的一部分没有被“隔离”，也没有警告坠落的标志。</p><p> “当然，我很震惊。我的右臀部受到了冲击，我的肩膀撞到了一块石头上。就在这时，一道闪电划过我的脑海。漆黑一片，我不知道自己正在坠落。什么都不会动。所以，我躺在那里，我说，“移动你的身体，宝贝，来吧，珍妮，移动你的身体。”然后，我打电话给我的朋友洛瑞。甚至连大口呼吸都很难尖叫，”她继续说道。</p><p> “当洛瑞跑去寻求帮助时，我听到了狮子的吼声，”她说。 “我最后的想法是，因为我是詹妮弗·刘易斯，‘这真是一个标题：国王吃了王后。詹妮弗·刘易斯的尸体碎片正被空运回美国。”</p><p>采访期间，展示了刘西斯在医院康复情况的图像和视频。刘易斯解释说，她已经完全康复，最近出现在詹妮弗·洛佩兹的最新作品<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jennifer-lopez-announces-new-album-and-film-this-is-me-now-3550010">《这就是我……现在：爱情故事》</a>中。</i></p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-ish-star-jenifer-lewis-nearly-died-after-falling-10-feet-into-ravine-3600758">《Black-ish》明星詹妮弗·刘易斯 (Jenifer Lewis) 跌入“10 英尺深的峡谷”后险些丧命</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
